	<li class="mb-1"> $\cos A=\dfrac{AB}{AC}=\dfrac{\sqrt{10}}{2}$;
	<li class="mb-1"> $\tan A=\dfrac{BC}{AB}=\dfrac{\sqrt{6}}{\sqrt{10}}$;
